g/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80bd113ae261a8e29321bc8315216a02635677ab","tid":2330753,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c90f1ff8023ac99c1bfa72e5269c51e9d531bd96","tid":2330753,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T09:13:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/4717\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_info%2F4717&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=06ed993d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/4717</a><br />\n<br />\n【612金鐘衝突】男子非法集結囚2周加刑到7個月 上訴庭指原判阻嚇度不足<br />\n<br />\n【頭條日報】33歲貴金屬貿易公司董事助理去年6月12日，在政府總部外與其他示威者搬動鐵馬到行車路，他早前承認非法集結罪，被判監兩周。律政司不滿刑罰過輕而申請刑期覆核，高等法院上訴庭上月裁定律政司的覆核理據成立，撤銷監禁兩周之刑期，改判監禁七個月。潘敏琦法官今在判詞中批評，原審裁判官林子勤判刑時只執著於案中沒有證供顯示實際有任何財物損失或破壞，亦沒有任何執勤的警員受傷，漠視控罪的控訴要旨是防患於未然。上訴庭強調判監兩周只是象徵性阻嚇，其懲罰性和阻嚇力度不足。（全文 ）<br />\n<br />\n資訊部按：潘官於判詞第43段尤如成語動畫廊般，使用大量成語及形容詞描繪示威場面及批評答辯人行為，指從「片段可見，當時警方與示威者的人數懸殊，擾攘的局面實屬沸沸騰騰，叫囂不絕，參與人士情緒極高漲，如箭在弦，隨時有一觸即發，一發不可收拾的危機。答辯人的作為，是把已經沸騰的局面，火上加油。正正就是羅敏聰案所指的給他人壯膽、吶喊助威」<br />\n<br />\nCAAR5/2020  判案理由書: <a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=132492&amp;currpage=T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Flrs%2Fcommon%2Fju%2Fju_frame.jsp%3FDIS%3D132492%26currpage%3DT&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=5366acf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=132492&amp;currpage=T</a> <br />\n<br />\n#20201218新聞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:38:04.000Z","msg":"唔敢寫英文判詞驚比其他common law judges恥笑個logic<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a376da008e8e6211eecb8536b478c114bfda0a","tid":2330753,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:38:17.000Z","msg":"哇，你老味，有無攪撚錯"},{"pid":"761f07af375f98c8ee058b379b3487404b258643","tid":2330753,"uid":359267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:45:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"medium\">狗官</span>"},{"pid":"dd6579d5a854b07a6a28ccdc90e31f14785415f8","tid":2330753,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80bd113ae261a8e29321bc8315216a02635677ab","tid":2330753,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c90f1ff8023ac99c1bfa72e5269c51e9d531bd96","tid":2330753,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T09:13:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/4717\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_info%2F4717&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=06ed993d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/4717</a><br />\n<br />\n【612金鐘衝突】男子非法集結囚2周加刑到7個月 上訴庭指原判阻嚇度不足<br />\n<br />\n【頭條日報】33歲貴金屬貿易公司董事助理去年6月12日，在政府總部外與其他示威者搬動鐵馬到行車路，他早前承認非法集結罪，被判監兩周。律政司不滿刑罰過輕而申請刑期覆核，高等法院上訴庭上月裁定律政司的覆核理據成立，撤銷監禁兩周之刑期，改判監禁七個月。潘敏琦法官今在判詞中批評，原審裁判官林子勤判刑時只執著於案中沒有證供顯示實際有任何財物損失或破壞，亦沒有任何執勤的警員受傷，漠視控罪的控訴要旨是防患於未然。上訴庭強調判監兩周只是象徵性阻嚇，其懲罰性和阻嚇力度不足。（全文 ）<br />\n<br />\n資訊部按：潘官於判詞第43段尤如成語動畫廊般，使用大量成語及形容詞描繪示威場面及批評答辯人行為，指從「片段可見，當時警方與示威者的人數懸殊，擾攘的局面實屬沸沸騰騰，叫囂不絕，參與人士情緒極高漲，如箭在弦，隨時有一觸即發，一發不可收拾的危機。答辯人的作為，是把已經沸騰的局面，火上加油。正正就是羅敏聰案所指的給他人壯膽、吶喊助威」<br />\n<br />\nCAAR5/2020  判案理由書: <a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=132492&amp;currpage=T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Flrs%2Fcommon%2Fju%2Fju_frame.jsp%3FDIS%3D132492%26currpage%3DT&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=5366acf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=132492&amp;currpage=T</a> <br />\n<br />\n#20201218新聞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:38:04.000Z","msg":"唔敢寫英文判詞驚比其他common law judges恥笑個logic<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:51:12.000Z","msg":"咁中文聆訊出中文判詞好正常嘅,但應該要整埋英文summary"},{"pid":"948a56cf4ca8c35acfbf7d4a790353db357798d0","tid":2330753,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a076425669fb5c26572c0fa6e96686916a952fa4","tid":2330753,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:37:13.000Z","msg":"個手足好似已經離境<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:51:40.000Z","msg":"另一單嚟, CAAR6"},{"pid":"27ff29b092e57b31d65a60b7fffe2954a33a3920","tid":2330753,"uid":170395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:57:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef63b1fea0897f0fd87012d244c6d4506675037","tid":2330753,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T11:07:59.000Z","msg":"有冇可能不停上訴刑期到終生監禁"},{"pid":"e84151c3e7d225b184219deb561c325f93efd617","tid":2330753,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd6579d5a854b07a6a28ccdc90e31f14785415f8","tid":2330753,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80bd113ae261a8e29321bc8315216a02635677ab","tid":2330753,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c90f1ff8023ac99c1bfa72e5269c51e9d531bd96","tid":2330753,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T09:13:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/4717\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_info%2F4717&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=06ed993d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/4717</a><br />\n<br />\n【612金鐘衝突】男子非法集結囚2周加刑到7個月 上訴庭指原判阻嚇度不足<br />\